      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1781461750197,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "We use the map here like, all the properties of the instricitc values are going to be in limited range means\nin the limited amount of the keys we can prepare lets say we have length widthh and color 3 options so\nwe will have 3*3*3 permutations, ok. So now we need to like 1|2|1 aisa karke we can prepare limted key and \nmap<key, FlyweightObject> , 10|10|Red|hard| key --> FlywrightObject , This map wala class is called \nflyweighFactory\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "We use the map here like, all the properties of the instricitc values are going to be in limited range means\nin the limited amount of the keys we can prepare lets say we have length widthh and color 3 options so\nwe will have 3*3*3 permutations, ok. So now we need to like 1|2|1 aisa karke we can prepare limted key and \nmap<key, FlyweightObject> , 10|10|Red|hard| key --> FlywrightObject , This map wala class is called \nflyweighFactory\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
